  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    VmsClientManager.VmsClientCallback
    Callback interface for Vehicle Map Service clients.
    VmsSubscriberManager.VmsSubscriberClientCallback
    Callback interface for Vehicle Map Service subscribers.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    VmsAssociatedLayer
    A Vehicle Map Service layer with a list of publisher IDs it is associated with.
    VmsAvailableLayers
    Availability of Vehicle Map Service layers.
    VmsClient
    API implementation for use by Vehicle Map Service clients.
    VmsClientManager
    Car Service manager for connecting clients to the Vehicle Map Service.
    VmsLayer
    A Vehicle Map Service layer, which can be offered or subscribed to by clients.
    VmsLayerDependency
    Layer dependencies for single Vehicle Map Service layer.
    VmsLayersOffering 已过时
    Use VmsClient.setProviderOfferings(int, Set) instead
    VmsOperationRecorder 已过时
    VmsOperationRecorder is no longer used by VMS and will produce no output
    VmsOperationRecorder.Writer  
    VmsProviderInfo
    Hidden data object used to communicate Vehicle Map Service publisher information on registration.
    VmsPublisherClientService 已过时
    Use VmsClientManager instead
    VmsRegistrationInfo
    Hidden data object used to communicate Vehicle Map Service client tokens and system state on client registration.
    VmsSubscriberManager 已过时
    Use VmsClientManager instead
    VmsSubscriptionHelper
    Internal utility for computing subscription updates.
    VmsSubscriptionState
    Subscription state of Vehicle Map Service layers.
